      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks for clarifying. That makes more sense. Could you look at this next part? I'm worried about the phrasing here:\n\n\"The Recipient shall be responsible for any and all indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages, including but not limited to loss of profits, loss of data, or business interruption, arising out of or in connection with any breach of this Agreement.\"\n\nDoes this mean I could be held liable for things that aren't even directly caused by my mistake, like their company losing potential future business? That seems really risky.",
